# Local development: SQLite is used automatically (no config needed)
# Run `npx convex dev` or simply `npm run dev` — SQLite runs locally.
#
# For Vercel deployment, set these environment variables in Vercel Dashboard:
#   TURSO_DATABASE_URL=libsql://your-db-name.turso.io
#   TURSO_AUTH_TOKEN=your-auth-token
#
# To pull env vars from Vercel to your local machine:
#   1. vercel link          (link project to Vercel)
#   2. vercel env pull .env.local   (download env vars)
#
# Or create a .env.local file manually:
# TURSO_DATABASE_URL=libsql://your-db-name.turso.io
# TURSO_AUTH_TOKEN=your-auth-token